quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,56,is roz badshahi khuda hi ki hogi. aur un mein faisla kardey ga to jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay woh Nemat ke baghoon mein hon ge
  22,57,aur jo kafir hue aur hamari ayaton ko jutlatay rahay un ke liye zaleel karne wala azaab hoga
  22,58,aur jin logon ne khuda ki raah mein hijrat ki phir maaray gay ya mar gay. un ko khuda achi rozi day ga. aur be shak khuda sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai
  22,59,woh un ko aisay maqam mein daakhil kere ga jisay woh pasand karen ge. aur khuda to jan-nay wala ( aur ) Burdbar hai
  22,60,yeh ( baat khuda ke haan thehr chuki hai ) aur jo shakhs ( kisi ko ) itni hi aeza day jitni aeza is ko di gayi phir is shakhs par zayad-ti ki jaye to khuda is ki madad kere ga. be shak khuda maaf karne wala aur bakhsnay wala hai
  22,61,yeh is liye ke khuda raat ko din mein daakhil kardaita hai aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai. aur khuda to suneney wala dekhnay wala hai
  22,62,yeh is liye ke khuda hi barhaq hai aur jis cheez ko ( kafir ) khuda ke siwa pkarte hain woh baatil hai aur is liye khuda Rafi al shan aur bara hai
  22,63,kiya tum nahi dekhte ke khuda aasman se meen barsata hai to zameen sirsabz hojati hai. be shak khuda bareek bain aur khabardaar hai
  22,64,jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai isi ka hai. aur be shak khuda be niaz aur qabil sataish hai .
